titleStmt.title: The case of John Prideaux Esq; Upon his petition against Francis Stratford Esq; the sitting member, for the borough of Newport, in the county of Cornwall. The petitioner complains of illegal and arbitrary proceedings of the vianders at the election; and of an undue return manifestly injurious to the petitioner.
titleStmt.author: Prideaux, John.
